      <title>對沖基金 Mountaineer Partners 敦促 Vishay 回購股票</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/hedge-fund-mountaineer-partners-urges-vishay-buy-back-shares-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社審閱的一封信函顯示，對沖基金 Mountaineer Partners 正在敦促分立電子元件製造商 Vishay Intertechnology 今年回購價值 6 億美元的股票，理由是該公司「估值過低」。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/hedge-fund-mountaineer-partners-urges-vishay-buy-back-shares-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:13:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
